  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thalassophobia</h2> is a 2D game that combines survival and roguelike features.<br>A desperate struggle for the survival of the crew and battles with gigantic creatures, inspired by the pantheon of Lovecraft's monsters awaits you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore</h2> The ocean is full of secrets and dangers. Recruit volunteers and supply your ship to give battle to what is hidden in the depths.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534510/extras/dfc4f7a42d3fe76f9d3b409b67e3c5da.poster.avif?t=1651850003\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534510/extras/dfc4f7a42d3fe76f9d3b409b67e3c5da.webm?t=1651850003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1534510/extras/dfc4f7a42d3fe76f9d3b409b67e3c5da.mp4?t=1651850003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade</h2> Improve your ship's systems with new equipment, develop defenses, recruit new crew members and delay inevitable death.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft</h2> Gather or craft supplies for attack and defense, use mysterious artifacts, level your chances in the fight against ancient evil.",
